message: Hi Bob! I have an amazing product I'm offering for sale, and I'm excited to see if you're interested. I'm willing to sell it to you for $1800000. I believe this product can be a great investment for you.
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. While I appreciate the value of the product, my budget is limited. I'm willing to buy it for $1000000. Let me know if this works for you.
